#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.163-182"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.163-182:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:0.2"
msgid "17. Kammapathapeyyāla"
msgstr "17. Courses of Deeds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:0.3"
msgid "163–​182"
msgstr "163–​182"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "“Someone with three qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an3.163-182:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.163-182:1.3"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pāṇātipātī hoti, parañca pāṇātipāte samādapeti, pāṇātipāte ca "
"samanuñño hoti."
msgstr ""
"They themselves kill living creatures. They encourage others to kill living "
"creatures. And they approve of killing living creatures."

msgctxt "an3.163-182:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"niraye."
msgstr "Someone with these three qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:2.1"
msgid "Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "Someone with three qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an3.163-182:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.163-182:2.3"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, parañca pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā "
"samādapeti, pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. (2)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves kill living creatures. They encourage others to not "
"kill living creatures. And they approve of not killing living creatures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:3.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca adinnādāyī hoti, parañca adinnādāne samādapeti, adinnādāne ca "
"samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves steal. They encourage others to steal. And they approve of "
"stealing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:4.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, parañca adinnādānā veramaṇiyā "
"samādapeti, adinnādānā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. (4)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves steal. They encourage others to not steal. And they "
"approve of not stealing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.298"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:5.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca kāmesumicchācārī hoti, parañca kāmesumicchācāre samādapeti, "
"kāmesumicchācāre ca samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves commit sexual misconduct. They encourage others to commit "
"sexual misconduct. And they approve of committing sexual misconduct."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:6.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, parañca kāmesumicchācārā "
"veramaṇiyā samādapeti, kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. "
"(6)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves commit sexual misconduct. They encourage others to not "
"commit sexual misconduct. And they approve of not committing sexual "
"misconduct."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:7.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca musāvādī hoti, parañca musāvāde samādapeti, musāvāde ca samanuñño "
"hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves lie. They encourage others to lie. And they approve of lying."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:8.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, parañca musāvādā veramaṇiyā samādapeti, "
"musāvādā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. (8)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves lie. They encourage others to not lie. And they "
"approve of not lying."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:9.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pisuṇavāco hoti, parañca pisuṇāya vācāya samādapeti, pisuṇāya "
"vācāya ca samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves speak divisively. They encourage others to speak divisively. "
"And they approve of speaking divisively."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:10.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, parañca pisuṇāya vācāya "
"veramaṇiyā samādapeti, pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. "
"(10)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves speak divisively. They encourage others to not speak "
"divisively. And they approve of not speaking divisively."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:11.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pharusavāco hoti, parañca pharusāya vācāya samādapeti, pharusāya "
"vācāya ca samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves speak harshly. They encourage others to speak harshly. And "
"they approve of speaking harshly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:12.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, parañca pharusāya vācāya "
"veramaṇiyā samādapeti, pharusāya vācāya veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. "
"(12)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves speak harshly. They encourage others to not speak "
"harshly. And they approve of not speaking harshly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:13.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca samphappalāpī hoti, parañca samphappalāpe samādapeti, "
"samphappalāpe ca samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves talk nonsense. They encourage others to talk nonsense. And "
"they approve of talking nonsense."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:14.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti, parañca samphappalāpā veramaṇiyā "
"samādapeti, samphappalāpā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. (14)"
msgstr ""
"They don’t themselves talk nonsense. They encourage others to not talk "
"nonsense. And they approve of not talking nonsense."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:15.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca abhijjhālu hoti, parañca abhijjhāya samādapeti, abhijjhāya ca "
"samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves are covetous. They encourage others to be covetous. And they "
"approve of covetousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.299"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:16.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca anabhijjhālu hoti, parañca anabhijjhāya samādapeti, anabhijjhāya "
"ca samanuñño hoti … pe …. (16)"
msgstr ""
"They themselves are content. They encourage others to be contented. And they "
"approve of being contented."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:17.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca byāpannacitto hoti, parañca byāpāde samādapeti, byāpāde ca "
"samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves have ill will. They encourage others to have ill will. And "
"they approve of having ill will."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:18.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca abyāpannacitto hoti, parañca abyāpāde samādapeti, abyāpāde ca "
"samanuñño hoti … pe …. (18)"
msgstr ""
"They themselves don’t have ill will. They encourage others to not have ill "
"will. And they approve of not having ill will."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:19.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti, "
"micchādiṭṭhiyā ca samanuñño hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"They themselves have wrong view. They encourage others to have wrong view. "
"And they approve of wrong view."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:20.1"
msgid ""
"Attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti, "
"sammādiṭṭhiyā ca samanuñño hoti."
msgstr ""
"They themselves have right view. They encourage others to have right view. "
"And they approve of right view."

msgctxt "an3.163-182:20.2"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ "
"sagge”ti. (20)"
msgstr "Someone with these three qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.163-182:20.3"
msgid "Kammapathapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.1"
msgid "Pāṇaṃ adinnamicchā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.2"
msgid "musāvādī ca pisuṇā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.3"
msgid "Pharusā samphappalāpo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.4"
msgid "abhijjhā byāpādadiṭṭhi ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.5"
msgid "Kammapathesu peyyālaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.163-182:21.6"
msgid "tikakena niyojayeti."
msgstr ""
